        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom:20px;"><label style="display:block;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.7);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px;">ご要望 / Special Requests</label><textarea id="r_message" rows="3" placeholder="Allergies, dietary requirements, special occasions..." style="width:100%;background:#1a1a1a;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.25);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;color:#f0ede4;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;resize:vertical;-webkit-appearance:none;"></textarea></div>

        <div style="background:rgba(201,169,110,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:11px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.5);line-height:1.7;">
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.7);font-weight:600;">キャンセルポリシー / Cancellation Policy</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 4px;">・24時間前以内：¥5,000 / person &nbsp;|&nbsp; Within 24 hours: ¥5,000 / person</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 10px;">・48時間前以内：¥2,500 / person &nbsp;|&nbsp; Within 48 hours: ¥2,500 / person</p>
          <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15);margin:8px 0;"/>
          <p style="margin:0 0 10px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.4);">※ このフォームでの送信は予約確定ではありません。{{ stores.brand.brand_name }} からの予約確定メールをお待ちください。<br/><br/>* This form does not confirm your reservation. Please wait for a confirmation email from {{ stores.brand.brand_name }}.</p>
          <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15);margin:8px 0;"/>
          {% if store.tel_display != 'TBD' %}
          <p style="margin:0;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.75);font-weight:600;">※ 当日予約の場合、お席の確認が遅れることがございますので、<a href="tel:{{ store.tel_raw }}" style="color:#c9a96e;text-decoration:underline;">{{ store.tel_display }}</a> までお電話ください。<br/><br/><span style="color:rgba(240,237,228,0.5);font-weight:400;">* For same-day reservations, seat confirmation may be delayed. Please call <a href="tel:{{ store.tel_raw }}" style="color:#c9a96e;text-decoration:underline;">{{ store.tel_display }}</a>.</span></p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div style="background:rgba(201,169,110,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:11px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.5);line-height:1.7;">
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.7);font-weight:600;">個人情報の取り扱いについて / Privacy Policy</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px;">ご入力いただいた個人情報(お名前・メールアドレス・電話番号等)は、ご予約の確認・連絡および当店からのお知らせのみに使用し、第三者に提供することはございません。法令に基づく場合を除き、お客様の同意なく目的外に利用することはありません。</p>
          <p style="margin:0;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.4);">* Personal information you provide (name, email, phone number, etc.) will be used solely for reservation confirmation, communication, and store notifications. We will not share your information with third parties except as required by law.</p>
        </div>

        <p id="r_error" style="color:#e57373;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:12px;display:none;"></p>
        <button onclick="openConfirmDialog()" id="r_submit" style="width:100%;background:#c9a96e;color:#090909;font-family:'Josefin Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:14px;border:none;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;">SEND REQUEST / 送信する</button>

        <p style="font-size:10px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.35);margin:10px 0 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.6;">送信することで、上記の個人情報の取り扱いに同意したものとみなされます。<br/>By submitting, you agree to the privacy terms above.</p>
      </div>

      {# Success screen — shown after EmailJS send succeeds #}
      <div id="reserveSuccess" style="display:none;">
        <div class="success-stage">
          <div class="gold-foil-bg"></div>
          <span class="gold-particle" style="left:20%;top:70%;--dx:15px;animation-delay:0.2s;"></span>
          <span class="gold-particle" style="left:35%;top:80%;--dx:-12px;animation-delay:0.6s;"></span>
          <span class="gold-particle" style="left:55%;top:75%;--dx:18px;animation-delay:1.0s;"></span>
          <span class="gold-particle" style="left:70%;top:82%;--dx:-10px;animation-delay:1.4s;"></span>
          <span class="gold-particle" style="left:82%;top:68%;--dx:14px;animation-delay:0.8s;"></span>
          <span class="gold-particle" style="left:15%;top:60%;--dx:-8px;animation-delay:1.8s;"></span>

          <svg class="sumi-brush-svg" id="sumiBrushSvg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M 28 22 Q 50 18 72 22"/>
            <path d="M 32 22 L 30 38"/>
            <path d="M 68 22 L 70 38"/>
            <path d="M 30 38 L 70 38"/>
            <path d="M 26 50 L 74 50"/>
            <path d="M 50 38 L 50 50"/>
            <path d="M 38 62 L 62 62"/>
            <path d="M 50 62 L 50 82"/>
            <path d="M 26 82 L 74 82"/>
          </svg>

          <h4 class="success-title" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:26px;color:#c9a96e;margin:0 0 8px;letter-spacing:0.05em;">Request Received</h4>
          <p class="success-title" style="font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.7);margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:0.15em;">ご予約リクエストを承りました</p>

          <div class="success-body" style="max-width:300px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(201,169,110,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);border-radius:12px;">
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.8);margin:0 0 10px;line-height:1.7;">
              {{ stores.brand.brand_name }} からの<br/>確定メールをお待ちください。
            </p>
            <div style="height:1px;background:rgba(201,169,110,0.2);margin:10px 0;"></div>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.55);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">
              Please wait for a confirmation<br/>from {{ stores.brand.brand_name }}.
            </p>
          </div>

          <button onclick="closeReserveModal()" class="success-close" style="margin-top:28px;background:transparent;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.5);color:#c9a96e;font-family:'Josefin Sans',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.2em;padding:11px 32px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(201,169,110,0.1)';this.style.borderColor='#c9a96e';" onmouseout="this.style.background='transparent';this.style.borderColor='rgba(201,169,110,0.5)';">CLOSE</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============================================================
     CONFIRMATION DIALOG (overlay on top of reservation modal)
     ============================================================ -->
<div id="confirmDialog" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:10000;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.75);overflow-y:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;">
  <div style="min-height:100%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:20px;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <div style="background:#0f0f0f;border:1.5px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.5);border-radius:16px;width:100%;max-width:440px;padding:28px 24px;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(201,169,110,0.15);">
      <button onclick="closeConfirmDialog()" style="position:absolute;top:14px;right:14px;background:none;border:none;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.5);font-size:22px;cursor:pointer;line-height:1;">&#x00D7;</button>

      <p style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.3em;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.6);text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px;">Final Check</p>
      <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:22px;color:#c9a96e;margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1.2;">Please Confirm Your Reservation</h3>
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.7);margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ご予約内容のご確認</p>

      <div style="background:rgba(201,169,110,0.08);border-left:3px solid #c9a96e;padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:18px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;">
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.8);margin:0 0 4px;line-height:1.6;">
          食材とお席の準備がございますので、内容に誤りがないかご確認ください。
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.5);margin:0;line-height:1.6;">
          We prepare ingredients and seating based on your reservation. Please confirm details are correct.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#1a1a1a;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.25);border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin-bottom:18px;">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);">
          <span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.6);text-transform:uppercase;">Date / 日付</span>
          <span id="confirm_date" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:20px;color:#c9a96e;font-weight:600;">—</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);">
          <span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.6);text-transform:uppercase;">Time / 時間</span>
          <span id="confirm_time" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:20px;color:#c9a96e;font-weight:600;">—</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);">
          <span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.6);text-transform:uppercase;">Guests / 人数</span>
          <span id="confirm_guests" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:20px;color:#c9a96e;font-weight:600;">—</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 0;gap:8px;">
          <span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:rgba(201,169,110,0.6);text-transform:uppercase;flex-shrink:0;">Course / コース</span>
          <span id="confirm_course" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:13px;color:#c9a96e;font-weight:600;text-align:right;line-height:1.4;">—</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
        <label style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;cursor:pointer;padding:10px 0;">
          <input id="confirm_check_details" type="checkbox" class="confirm-checkbox"/>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.75);line-height:1.5;">
            <strong style="color:rgba(201,169,110,0.9);font-weight:600;">日付・時間・人数を確認しました</strong><br/>
            <span style="color:rgba(240,237,228,0.55);font-size:11px;">I have confirmed the date, time and number of guests are correct.</span>
          </span>
        </label>
        <label style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;cursor:pointer;padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);">
          <input id="confirm_check_policy" type="checkbox" class="confirm-checkbox"/>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(240,237,228,0.75);line-height:1.5;">
            <strong style="color:rgba(201,169,110,0.9);font-weight:600;">キャンセルポリシーを確認しました</strong><br/>
            <span style="color:rgba(240,237,228,0.55);font-size:11px;">I have read and agree to the cancellation policy.</span>
          </span>
        </label>
      </div>

      <p id="confirm_error" style="color:#e57373;font-size:11px;margin:0 0 12px;display:none;">両方にチェックを入れてください / Please check both boxes.</p>

      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.2fr;gap:10px;">
        <button onclick="closeConfirmDialog()" style="background:transparent;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.4);color:rgba(201,169,110,0.9);font-family:'Josefin Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:13px 10px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;">修正する<br/><span style="font-size:9px;opacity:0.7;">EDIT</span></button>
        <button onclick="confirmAndSubmit()" id="confirm_submit_btn" style="background:#c9a96e;color:#090909;font-family:'Josefin Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:13px 10px;border:none;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;">この内容で送信<br/><span style="font-size:9px;opacity:0.75;">CONFIRM &amp; SEND</span></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- EmailJS SDK -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@emailjs/browser@4/dist/email.min.js"></script>

<script>
(function(){
  // ============================================================
  // Store-specific config injected from _data/stores.js
  // ============================================================
  var EMAILJS_CFG = {
    public_key:        '{{ store.form_config.emailjs.public_key }}',
    service_id:        '{{ store.form_config.emailjs.service_id }}',
    template_id_owner: '{{ store.form_config.emailjs.template_id_owner }}',
    template_id_guest: '{{ store.form_config.emailjs.template_id_guest }}'
  };
  var STORE_INFO = {
    location:     '{{ store.name_jp }}',
    location_key: '{{ store.slug }}',
    address_jp:   '{{ store.address_jp_line1 }}',
    address_en:   '{{ store.address_en_line1 }}'
  };
  var BLOCKED_DATES = [];
  {% if store.form_config and store.form_config.blocked_dates %}
    {% for d in store.form_config.blocked_dates %}
  BLOCKED_DATES.push('{{ d }}');
    {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}

  // Initialize EmailJS
  if (typeof emailjs !== 'undefined' && EMAILJS_CFG.public_key) {
    emailjs.init(EMAILJS_CFG.public_key);
  }

  // ============================================================
  // Course card radio selection
  // ============================================================
  window.selectCourse = function(courseId) {
    var ids = ['sumi', 'bokuga', 'bokushou'];
    ids.forEach(function(id) {
      var card = document.getElementById('course-card-' + id);
      if (!card) return;
      var radio = card.querySelector('input[type="radio"]');
      if (id === courseId) {
        card.classList.add('selected');
        radio.checked = true;
        document.getElementById('r_course').value = radio.value;
      } else {
        card.classList.remove('selected');
        radio.checked = false;
      }
    });
  };

  // ============================================================
  // Open / Close modal
  // ============================================================
  window.openReserveModal = function(label) {
    document.getElementById('reserveModal').style.display = 'block';
    document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
    window._reserveModalOpenedAt = Date.now();

    var today = new Date();
    var minDate = today.getFullYear() + '-' +
                  String(today.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0') + '-' +
                  String(today.getDate()).padStart(2,'0');
    document.getElementById('r_date').setAttribute('min', minDate);

    // GA4 event
    if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
      gtag('event', 'reserve_modal_open', {
        'event_category': 'engagement',
        'event_label': label,
        'store_name': '{{ store.slug }}',
        'store_area': '{{ store.region }}',
        'brand': '{{ stores.brand.brand_slug }}',
        'channel': '{{ store.channel_id }}'
      });
    }
    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
    window.dataLayer.push({
      event: 'reserve_modal_open',
      reserve_button_location: label
    });
  };

  window.closeReserveModal = function() {
    document.getElementById('reserveModal').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('confirmDialog').style.display = 'none';
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
    document.getElementById('reserveForm').style.display = 'block';
    document.getElementById('reserveSuccess').style.display = 'none';
    var brushReset = document.getElementById('sumiBrushSvg');
    if (brushReset) brushReset.classList.remove('drawing');
    ['r_name','r_email','r_phone','r_course','r_guests','r_time','r_date','r_message','r_website'].forEach(function(id){
      var el = document.getElementById(id);
      if (el) el.value = '';
    });
    ['sumi','bokuga','bokushou'].forEach(function(id) {
      var card = document.getElementById('course-card-' + id);
      if (card) {
        card.classList.remove('selected');
        var radio = card.querySelector('input[type="radio"]');
        if (radio) radio.checked = false;
      }
    });
    var cd1 = document.getElementById('confirm_check_details');
    var cd2 = document.getElementById('confirm_check_policy');
    if (cd1) cd1.checked = false;
    if (cd2) cd2.checked = false;
    var err = document.getElementById('r_error');
    if (err) { err.style.display = 'none'; err.textContent = ''; }
    var btn = document.getElementById('r_submit');
    if (btn) { btn.textContent = 'SEND REQUEST / 送信する'; btn.disabled = false; }
  };

  // ============================================================
  // Date validation against blocked dates
  // ============================================================
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    var dateInput = document.getElementById('r_date');
    if (dateInput && BLOCKED_DATES.length) {
      dateInput.addEventListener('change', function() {
        if (BLOCKED_DATES.indexOf(this.value) !== -1) {
          alert('申し訳ございません。選択された日付は予約を受付しておりません。\n\nSorry, the selected date is unavailable. Please select another date.');
          this.value = '';
        }
      });
    }
  });

  // ============================================================
  // Open confirmation dialog
  // ============================================================
  window.openConfirmDialog = function() {
    var name    = document.getElementById('r_name').value.trim();
    var email   = document.getElementById('r_email').value.trim();
    var phone   = document.getElementById('r_phone').value.trim();
    var course  = document.getElementById('r_course').value;
    var guests  = document.getElementById('r_guests').value;
    var time    = document.getElementById('r_time').value;
    var date    = document.getElementById('r_date').value;
    var website = document.getElementById('r_website').value.trim();
    var errEl   = document.getElementById('r_error');

    // Honeypot trip → silently "succeed"
    if (website !== '') {
      document.getElementById('reserveForm').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('reserveSuccess').style.display = 'block';
      var brushSvg1 = document.getElementById('sumiBrushSvg');
      if (brushSvg1) { brushSvg1.classList.remove('drawing'); void brushSvg1.offsetWidth; brushSvg1.classList.add('drawing'); }
      return;
    }
    // Speed-trap: submitted too quickly → silent success
    var openedAt = window._reserveModalOpenedAt || 0;
    if (Date.now() - openedAt < 3000) {
      document.getElementById('reserveForm').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('reserveSuccess').style.display = 'block';
      var brushSvg2 = document.getElementById('sumiBrushSvg');
      if (brushSvg2) { brushSvg2.classList.remove('drawing'); void brushSvg2.offsetWidth; brushSvg2.classList.add('drawing'); }
      return;
    }

    if (!name || !email || !phone || !course || !guests || !time || !date) {
      errEl.textContent = '* 必須項目を入力してください / Please fill in required fields.';
      errEl.style.display = 'block';
      return;
    }
    if (BLOCKED_DATES.indexOf(date) !== -1) {
      errEl.textContent = '※ 選択された日付は予約を受付しておりません / The selected date is unavailable.';
      errEl.style.display = 'block';
      return;
    }
    errEl.style.display = 'none';

    var dateObj = new Date(date);
    var weekdays = ['Sun','Mon','Tue','Wed','Thu','Fri','Sat'];
    var formattedDate = dateObj.getFullYear() + '/' +
                        String(dateObj.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0') + '/' +
                        String(dateObj.getDate()).padStart(2,'0') +
                        ' (' + weekdays[dateObj.getDay()] + ')';

    document.getElementById('confirm_date').textContent = formattedDate;
    document.getElementById('confirm_time').textContent = time;
    document.getElementById('confirm_guests').textContent = guests + (guests === '1' ? ' guest' : ' guests');
    document.getElementById('confirm_course').textContent = course.split(' - ')[0];

    document.getElementById('confirm_check_details').checked = false;
    document.getElementById('confirm_check_policy').checked = false;
    document.getElementById('confirm_error').style.display = 'none';

    document.getElementById('confirmDialog').style.display = 'block';
  };

  window.closeConfirmDialog = function() {
    document.getElementById('confirmDialog').style.display = 'none';
  };

  // ============================================================
  // Submit via EmailJS
  // ============================================================
  window.confirmAndSubmit = async function() {
    var checkDetails = document.getElementById('confirm_check_details').checked;
    var checkPolicy  = document.getElementById('confirm_check_policy').checked;
    var errEl = document.getElementById('confirm_error');

    if (!checkDetails || !checkPolicy) {
      errEl.textContent = '両方にチェックを入れてください / Please check both boxes.';
      errEl.style.display = 'block';
      return;
    }
    errEl.style.display = 'none';

    var btn = document.getElementById('confirm_submit_btn');
    btn.textContent = 'Sending...';
    btn.disabled = true;

    var params = {
      name:    document.getElementById('r_name').value.trim(),
      email:   document.getElementById('r_email').value.trim(),
      phone:   document.getElementById('r_phone').value.trim(),
      course:  document.getElementById('r_course').value,
      guests:  document.getElementById('r_guests').value,
      time:    document.getElementById('r_time').value,
      date:    document.getElementById('r_date').value,
      message: document.getElementById('r_message').value.trim(),
      source_path:  window.location.pathname,
      location:     STORE_INFO.location,
      location_key: STORE_INFO.location_key,
      address_jp:   STORE_INFO.address_jp,
      address_en:   STORE_INFO.address_en
    };

    try {
      await emailjs.send(EMAILJS_CFG.service_id, EMAILJS_CFG.template_id_owner, params);
      await emailjs.send(EMAILJS_CFG.service_id, EMAILJS_CFG.template_id_guest, params);

      // GA4 / dataLayer
      if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
        gtag('event', 'reservation_form_submit', {
          'event_category': 'conversion',
          'form_guests': params.guests,
          'form_date': params.date,
          'form_course': params.course,
          'store_name': '{{ store.slug }}',
          'store_area': '{{ store.region }}',
          'brand': '{{ stores.brand.brand_slug }}',
          'channel': '{{ store.channel_id }}'
        });
      }
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      window.dataLayer.push({
        event: 'reservation_form_submit',
        form_guests: params.guests,
        form_date: params.date,
        form_course: params.course,
        source_path: params.source_path
      });

      document.getElementById('confirmDialog').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('reserveForm').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('reserveSuccess').style.display = 'block';
      var brushSvg = document.getElementById('sumiBrushSvg');
      if (brushSvg) {
        brushSvg.classList.remove('drawing');
        void brushSvg.offsetWidth;
        brushSvg.classList.add('drawing');
      }
    } catch (err) {
      errEl.textContent = 'エラーが発生しました。再度お試しください。/ An error occurred. Please try again.';
      errEl.style.display = 'block';
      btn.innerHTML = 'この内容で送信<br/><span style="font-size:9px;opacity:0.75;">CONFIRM &amp; SEND</span>';
      btn.disabled = false;
    }
  };

  // ============================================================
  // Close modal by clicking outside
  // ============================================================
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    var m = document.getElementById('reserveModal');
    if (m) m.addEventListener('click', function(e){ if (e.target === this) closeReserveModal(); });
    var cd = document.getElementById('confirmDialog');
    if (cd) cd.addEventListener('click', function(e){ if (e.target === this) closeConfirmDialog(); });
  });
})();
</script>
